inputs.text: You are an assistant designed to generate high quality anime images based on textual prompts. <Prompt Start> @comfyanonymous, "Make me a desktop image of a beautiful barefoot woman's silhouette walking through a noir city street at dusk. A melancholic anime-style illustration showing her silhouette moving through rain-slicked streets lined with neon signs and tall buildings. The color palette is predominantly cool tones: deep navy blues (#2E3440, #3B4252), steel grays (#4C566A), and pale sky blues (#88C0D0, #8FBCBB), with occasional neon accents reflecting off wet pavement. The noir cityscape shows towering buildings, fire escapes, and street lights creating atmospheric fog and shadow. Soft ambient lighting from neon signs and street lamps creates a contemplative, lo-fi aesthetic. The art style should be minimalist with clean lines, subtle grain texture, and a nostalgic, introspective mood. Her bare feet should be visible as she walks through the urban landscape under a twilight sky with subtle cloud streaks."
